.IntroDialogue2":"Why don't we just go guns blazing from the get-go? Beats me. ¥n These are the instructions we were given.","Location.Graveyard":"the graveyard","Notification.MissionFailed":"Mission Failed","Operator.Any.DisguiseFound":"This robe is torn, but I might be able to patch it up...","Location.Tower":"the tower","Operator.Any.EnteredLabDialogue3":"I don't know what to expect anymore ¥n I've got to be careful...","Location.TowerEntrance":"the tower entrance","ItemDesc.Empty":"Empty","Objective.Mission5":"Open the Vault","Hacking.AuthorizeDesc":"AUTHORIZE - Authorize the opening of the vault","Location.Backyard":"the backyard","Action.Sew":"Sew","Objective.TakedownLimit":"Incapacitating a Priest will raise the Alarm","Operator.Any.PickedThermite1":"So...do any of you know what this thermite is for? No? ¥n Is upper management pulling some sort of prank on us?","Notification.Cutscene3":"TREMBLES","Location.LabHallway":"the lab hallway","Name.DemonSpawn":"Demon Spawn","Notification.Cutscene1":"THE","ItemDesc.Cloth":"A small piece of fabric","Operator.Any.IntroDialogue":"Remember our plan. I'll give you a signal if I'm compromised ¥n So you better pay attention to your radios.","Location.Yard":"the yard","Location.Shed":"the shed","Objective.UnlockShed":"Unlock the Shed","Location.Lab":"the lab","Notification.CodeFound":"Found the Safe Combination","Operator.Any.ShedFound1":"That's a tough lock.","Location.Vault":"the vault","Location.LabEntrance":"the lab entrance","Name.Scientist":"Scientist","Hack.OfficePriestDiversion":"Divert the Priest to the Laboratory","Name.OccultistRobe":"Occultist Robe","Objective.Mission9":"Place the Thermite","Hack.CheckpointGuardDiversion":"Divert the Checkpoint Guard to the Office","Location.Staircase":"the staircase","Location.Dorms":"the dorms","Location.Entrance":"the entrance","Location.Checkpoint":"the checkpoint","Notification.Cutscene5":"TERROR","Operator.Any.InspectedGooDialogue2":"A viscous substance. It looks like muscl